stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CLOSED : initial state

    CLOSED --> CLOSED : call success

    CLOSED --> OPEN : failure rate >= 50%\nmin 5 calls required\n\ncounted as failure\n  IOException\n  TimeoutException\n  WebClient 5xx / BadGateway / GatewayTimeout\n\nignored (not counted)\n  WebClient 4xx (BadRequest, Unprocessable)

    OPEN --> OPEN : CallNotPermittedException\n-> immediate 503 (fast fail)\nwait duration 30s

    OPEN --> HALF_OPEN : 30s elapsed\n3 probe calls permitted

    HALF_OPEN --> CLOSED : all 3 probes succeed\n-> recovered

    HALF_OPEN --> OPEN : any probe fails\n-> wait 30s again
